FILE REQUEST:
    -----------------------------------------------------------------
    |             |                                                 |
    |   'file'    |   full path(/home/johnson/Pictures/sell.png)    |
    |   String    |                    String                       |
    -----------------------------------------------------------------
FILE RESPONSE:
    ---------------------------------------------------------------------
    |           |           |               |           |               |
    |   MAGIC   |   length  |   fileName    |   length  |   contents    |
    |    int    |    int    |    String     |    int    |     bytes     |
    ---------------------------------------------------------------------

QUERY REQUEST:
    -------------------------------------
    |           |           |           |
    |   'query' |     id    |   field   |
    |   String  |    int    |    int    |
    -------------------------------------
QUERY RESPONSE:
    ---------------------------------------------
    |               |           |               |
    |   MediaType   |   length  |   contents    |
    |      int      |    int    |    String     |
    ---------------------------------------------

ADD REQUEST:
    -----------------------------------------------------------------
    |           |           |           |           |               |
    |   'add'   |   fields  |   field   |   length  |   contents    |
    |   String  |    int    |    int    |     int   |    String     |
    -----------------------------------------------------------------
ADD RESPONSE:
    ---------------------------------------------
    |               |           |               |
    |   MediaType   |   length  |   contents    |
    |      int      |    int    |    String     |
    ---------------------------------------------

EDIT REQUEST:
    -------------------------------------------------------------
    |           |       |           |           |               |
    |   'edit'  |   id  |   field   |   length  |   contents    |
    |   String  |  int  |    int    |     int   |    String     |
    -------------------------------------------------------------
EDIT RESPONSE:
    ---------------------------------------------
    |               |           |               |
    |   MediaType   |   length  |   contents    |
    |      int      |    int    |    String     |
    ---------------------------------------------

DELETE REQUEST:
    -------------------------
    |               |       |
    |   'delete'    |   id  |
    |    String     |   int |
    -------------------------
DELETE RESPONSE:
    ---------------------------------------------
    |               |           |               |
    |   MediaType   |   length  |   contents    |
    |     int       |    int    |    String     |
    ---------------------------------------------